    "# Part 1: Real Life Examples and Simpson's Paradox\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook addresses Part 1a (confounders, colliders, mediation) and Part 1b (Simpson's paradox)."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 12,
